driving-tooltip: For automotive routing. This profile shows the fastest routes by preferring high-speed roads like highways.
driving-traffic-tooltip: For automotive routing. This profile factors in current and historic traffic conditions to avoid slowdowns.
cycling-tooltip: For bicycle routing. This profile shows routes that are short and safer for cyclists by avoiding highways and preferring streets with bike lanes.
walking-tooltip: For pedestrian and hiking routing. This profile shows the shortest path by using sidewalks and trails.
